CodeList.Name: Subject Status Test Name

Description.TranslatedText: Terminology relevant to test name for subject characteristics that are evaluated periodically to determine if they have changed.

EnumeratedItem.nciodm:CDISCDefinition: The state or condition of being living or deceased; also includes the case where the vital status is unknown.
